---
import PageHero from '../../components/astro/PageHero.astro'
import PageShell from '../../components/astro/PageShell.astro'

const pillars = [
  ['Clarity', 'We turn scattered financial details into clean records, practical insights, and decisions people can use.'],
  ['Trust', 'We build consistent systems, careful communication, and long-term relationships grounded in reliability.'],
  ['Calm', 'We reduce the noise around deadlines, documents, compliance, and systems so clients can think clearly.'],
]

const audiences = [
  ['Established businesses', 'Companies ready to move from basic bookkeeping to more strategic financial management.'],
  ['Modern founders', 'Entrepreneurs who use technology and need an equally organized partner around finance, payroll, and scale.'],
  ['Professional firms', 'Agencies, consultants, practices, and service businesses that need clean records and practical tax planning.'],
  ['Asset-heavy operators', 'Real estate and operational businesses navigating cash flow, compliance, and long-term planning.'],
]

const feelings = [
  ['Relieved', 'The burden of financial guesswork feels lighter because records, deadlines, and next steps are organized.'],
  ['Secure', 'Clients know their information is handled carefully, ethically, and with professional discipline.'],
  ['Clear-headed', 'Clean data and plain-English guidance help owners understand where they stand and what to consider next.'],
  ['Respected', 'Communication is calm, transparent, and mindful of the client’s time.'],
]
---

<PageShell active="about">
  <PageHero eyebrow="About Fidara" title="Built on trust, clarity, and calm financial structure." description="Fidara exists for people and businesses who want their financial lives to feel more organized, intentional, and understandable." backgroundImage="/images/about.png" />
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr]">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">The name</p>
        <h2 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight text-slate-900">Fidara begins with trust.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-5 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700">
        <p>The name Fidara is inspired by Fides, a root associated with trust, faith, and reliability. The modern ending points toward clarity, direction, and forward motion.</p>
        <p>That combination reflects the role Fidara aims to play for clients: a steady financial partner that helps turn complexity into a clearer, more predictable path forward.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      {pillars.map(([title, description]) => (
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900">{title}</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">{description}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white/60 p-8 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">Our story</p>
      <h2 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight text-slate-900">We were built for clients who need more than reactive filing or basic data entry.</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700 md:grid-cols-2">
        <p>Every business has a vision, but the path toward it is often crowded by operational noise: messy records, tax deadlines, payroll questions, disconnected systems, and compliance uncertainty.</p>
        <p>Fidara brings accounting, tax, payroll, advisory, U.S. expansion, and managed technology support into one calmer relationship. We help clients understand the numbers that matter so they can move forward with more confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-4">
      {audiences.map(([title, description]) => (
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl leading-tight text-slate-900">{title}</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">{description}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">How clients should feel</p>
        <h2 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight text-slate-900">Relieved, secure, clear-headed, and respected.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        {feelings.map(([title, description]) => (
          <article class="border-t border-stone-200 pt-5">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl leading-tight text-slate-900">{title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">{description}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 px-8 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl rounded-xl border border-emerald-900/10 bg-emerald-950 p-8 text-white shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-100">The people behind the work</p>
      <h2 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight">A coordinated team around your financial and operational life.</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-emerald-50">Fidara’s work is delivered through professionals focused on accounting, tax coordination, payroll workflows, advisory conversations, technology systems, and client communication. As the firm grows, this page can expand into individual bios while keeping the same clear, grounded voice.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageShell>
